{"tid":997534,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"摩洛哥13天遊","createTime":"2019-01-27T08:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T04:44:03.000Z","uid":205326,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0f0faa1b2922873d829d19d7d2f72ef73a0f66bd","tid":997534,"uid":205326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T08:57:50.000Z","msg":"摩洛哥13天遊<br />\n其實只係想開個post 記錄呢段旅程，話哂都叫去左非洲，所以文筆麻麻請見諒。<br />\n由21/1/2019 - 3/1/2019 (2號係摩洛哥上機，3號番到香港)<br />\n我地 total 兩個人，撘lufthansa airline, 先由香港飛去瑞士（13個鐘) 之後等6個鐘，再由瑞士飛摩洛哥 Marrakech (4個鐘), 因為買個陣特價$3800來回，所以真係好抵屌。去之後換左美金同歐元，因為摩洛哥既貨幣唔會流出去，只可以到埗先換，而且唔接受港幣<br />\n<br />\n大約路線係Marrakech &gt;Sahara desert &gt;Fes &gt; chefchaouen &gt;Tangier &gt; Asilah &gt;Casablanca &gt; Marrakech"},{"pid":"6494ff019f090b563e8014f1c324a8cfa74b10c4","tid":997534,"uid":205326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:00:46.000Z","msg":"Day 1 <br />\n飛到瑞士出左境，去city 食左個$200 既早餐再周圍行下就番翻機場，<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xFqwEWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxFqwEWr.png&h=045ea39e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yP7CAuO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyP7CAuO.png&h=717a5d92&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MwrDjWt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMwrDjWt.png&h=4feb13da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6AEJv3a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6AEJv3a.png&h=77a1d38c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8279f88ba3d46c36c92c5d99696b1d4d1b500b3","tid":997534,"uid":205326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:05:13.000Z","msg":"上到細機話機件有問題，delay 左一個鐘，到Marrakech 已經係5點，訂左酒店接送，出舊城區大約15分鐘就到酒店，黎到摩洛哥好小人會去住酒店，通常都會住Riad 。<br />\n<br />\n經過24小時長征終於到第一間Riad！通常黎到Riad 佢地都會比薄荷菜同曲奇餅比你，我就覺得好似飲緊牙膏，但我朋友就好鐘意。btw 摩洛哥周圍都係靚貓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7FJ2MCV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7FJ2MCV.png&h=4e10f81b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ufGzCJY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FufGzCJY.png&h=c4d7edb2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wOcOHaF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwOcOHaF.png&h=0e87abd5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NaVsXJ2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNaVsXJ2.png&h=e375cd57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"371d9cf309e3563035aa124d372f90dade14c0e1","tid":997534,"uid":205326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:09:22.000Z","msg":"因為都6點幾，所以求其係酒店隔離餐廳食d野就番房訓。食左$150港幣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w6c3v50.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw6c3v50.png&h=f465276b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3dLwEZn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3dLwEZn.png&h=892065e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"604de4c016f94368e3efcca88f9b261b750af33e","tid":997534,"uid":47422,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:09:46.000Z","msg":"【旅行慘死】兩女遊客陳屍摩洛哥山區 一遭斬首一遭割喉<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181219/59046342\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181219%2F59046342&d=IaL90kcc6RX%2FizET26T3O9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=729bc613\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181219%2F59046342&h=c98bec92\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181219/59046342</a>"},{"pid":"a35e31ba2ebd54cd775321a888befc05710afd51","tid":997534,"uid":205326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"604de4c016f94368e3efcca88f9b261b750af33e","tid":997534,"uid":47422,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:09:46.000Z","msg":"【旅行慘死】兩女遊客陳屍摩洛哥山區 一遭斬首一遭割喉<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181219/59046342\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181219%2F59046342&d=IaL90kcc6RX%2FizET26T3O9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=729bc613\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181219%2F59046342&h=c98bec92\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181219/59046342</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:15:30.000Z","msg":"個到係山區，我地去既都係旅遊景點，入黑前我地就番酒店，係舊城會叫酒店staff 接我地，其實小心d係沒問題。"},{"pid":"d8778a39e281808e16d6661df25c14a504d7b28c","tid":997534,"uid":205326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:55:46.000Z","msg":"Day 2 <br />\n9點幾左右就自然醒左，係riad 食左麥皮就出發去 Majorelle Garden( ysl garden) ，因為我地既riad 係舊城同新城中間，search 左google maps 話行20分鐘所以我地就試下行過去，可能係朝早，街比我地想像中安全，當然我地銀包貴重野都係拎係前面，行過去既時候順便買埋ctm 巴士同火車票，跟住google maps 行大路，大約15分鐘就行到，我地去Majorelle garden 同YSL Museum, total 170 dr 一個人 (hkd$140)，其實都幾貴，garden 同museum 都好細，如果唔係要影相，15分鐘可以行哂.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wCgWRmt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwCgWRmt.png&h=925ebaea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xM6LKGv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxM6LKGv.png&h=9a64f222&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k6uJwmy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk6uJwmy.png&h=cef2ffd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24ef1f088bdd829003d9d866a240a696f5767b8e","tid":997534,"uid":16697,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f1961fa68b20c4ec26e3a841d1b058a9465813","tid":997534,"uid":205326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"24ef1f088bdd829003d9d866a240a696f5767b8e","tid":997534,"uid":16697,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T22:27:24.000Z","msg":"啱啊，特別係Fes <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d033f061589b10de1f638f097d515f4fc94255","tid":997534,"uid":67676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f0f1961fa68b20c4ec26e3a841d1b058a9465813","tid":997534,"uid":205326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"24ef1f088bdd829003d9d866a240a696f5767b8e","tid":997534,"uid":16697,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T22:27:24.000Z","msg":"啱啊，特別係Fes <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:57:32.000Z","msg":"真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個感覺好差<br />\n所有人都喺度打緊你主意<br />\n<br />\n值得去一次 但值得再去"},{"pid":"d3f3c5a081d2e5ba757b8ac1fa2e620df42dd51b","tid":997534,"uid":23560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T07:17:35.000Z","msg":"留名等睇報sahara tour嘅部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b484a60145cfc1e68bcfc252eae6e95104c792b8","tid":997534,"uid":205326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T18:40:26.000Z","msg":"之後去左舊城square 行左陣街，買左兩條圍巾兩件衫去沙漠著，同食左蝸牛就翻riad 食杯麵，第二日出發去沙漠！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JZ4UaH3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJZ4UaH3.png&h=c6932629&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QOv4xWq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQOv4xWq.png&h=c849b6e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b79cae08bd8571670ff836d7b7a375da0edda43","tid":997534,"uid":205326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T18:51:16.000Z","msg":"Day 3 沙漠團<br />\n今次我報咗豪華團,因為計左普通團大約一千港幣但唔包去fes (普通團通常都Marrakech 去Marrakech ), 係中間點drop 低你，自己拼的士可能都要400-500 (兩個人), 同埋check 天氣好似唔係幾好，所以就係馬蜂窩報左豪華拼團(Marrakech 去Fes走)，1850 人仔一個人，三日兩夜包早晚"},{"pid":"65318146294f9ad9333959c29f7f1a7768412325","tid":997534,"uid":205326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T19:04:17.000Z","msg":"今日重點行程就係權力遊戲取景地點 Ait- Ben- Haddou. 其實冇咩特別，之後就翻左酒店<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DvtE6pj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDvtE6pj.png&h=3e11e58a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7dthS4k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7dthS4k.png&h=49563ff4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MM724a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMM724a0.png&h=9bbb0337&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8xGn4a1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8xGn4a1.png&h=75654eaa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a21e23f7f4b9ccc63a5ccd9571855ad82a75738c","tid":997534,"uid":205326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T05:16:00.000Z","msg":"Day 4 撒哈拉沙漠<br />\n大約8點出發，先會去一個canyon 既地方睇下，之後食個lunch ，就直接去撒哈拉沙漠(途中停左個地方俾我地著d民族衫影左張相)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KVTE9Na.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKVTE9Na.png&h=89589dea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iWdqkTR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiWdqkTR.png&h=7b133c84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CNwvw1t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCNwvw1t.png&h=1110d626&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5984b53cbc76d520ff9da5b3649c7976873b49ca","tid":997534,"uid":81211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24ef1f088bdd829003d9d866a240a696f5767b8e","tid":997534,"uid":16697,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T05:26:45.000Z","msg":"同伊斯坦堡比，邊個多呃神騙鬼多D?"},{"pid":"e277f0441cf2cfe7d2932fd52774dc3ecba2a599","tid":997534,"uid":205326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:16:07.000Z","msg":"大約5點就到沙漠口，應該普通團同豪華團都係呢個時間先入沙漠，見到沙漠係真心覺得好壯觀，天氣都超級好，騎住駱駝入營地邊睇日落，騎到條腰好攰同埋每次落斜都淆淆地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4p0gsUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4p0gsUk.png&h=e551381d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mv3xLF1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmv3xLF1.png&h=4e2a79ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d4F8i02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd4F8i02.png&h=f34e386c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HFBn7Un.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHFBn7Un.png&h=eedaa0d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n騎左15分鐘左右就到左營地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vMBSLGr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvMBSLGr.png&h=2d2b38a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d57e6b0c40b905c9dedfb09a73f9f95d6143adf","tid":997534,"uid":205326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:36:43.000Z","msg":"營地係比我想像仲要好，分比我地個營total 兩張單人床，一張雙人床(我地得兩個人),獨立廁所，有無限熱水沖涼，有wifi<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/seqoSom.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FseqoSom.png&h=4b252a24&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x6gvxon.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx6gvxon.png&h=bff107e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢到就係普通團同豪華團最大分別:<br />\n普通團就冇獨立廁所，好似冇得沖涼，同埋佢唔會比你帶行李入沙漠，導遊會叫你執定一個背囊入營，gip 會放係大巴到。<br />\n豪華團就會幫你車埋大gip 入沙漠，時間比較有彈性，好似我地同導遊講我地想買酒入沙漠飲，佢就帶我地去。同埋好似普通團第二日就7點左右就會離開沙漠，豪華就9點半左右 (呢個唔係好sure )<br />\n天氣好加靚景真係點影都靚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a37Oi77.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa37Oi77.png&h=4ee9b91f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0OXiGmt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0OXiGmt.png&h=f1b6dde3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gtAoSs9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgtAoSs9.png&h=d21b9c51&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JOLTve8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJOLTve8.png&h=67d5f819&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R2sOi8t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR2sOi8t.png&h=0f0687a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MYjkUGP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMYjkUGP.png&h=510743e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LHHiGmQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLHHiGmQ.png&h=f1d1781d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fb13a20b507e6e2724cba1a28668596fec714b1","tid":997534,"uid":155756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T18:10:35.000Z","msg":"想問下有無沙漠團ge details <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果可以可唔可以tg <a href=\"https://t.me/jca_t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjca_t&d=IaL90kcc6RX%2FizET26T3O9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=f0ecf0cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/jca_t</a><br />\nThanks so much !"},{"pid":"ff7adcaa319db05f324ed848588200d31b617e25","tid":997534,"uid":140032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:51:51.000Z","msg":"仲有冇多啲介紹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree